snippet.title: sm64coopdx v1.0 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD THE GAME: https://github.com/coop-deluxe/sm64coopdx/releases/latest
DOWNLOAD MODS:
https://mods.sm64coopdx.com

After about 6 months in the making, sm64coopdx v1.0 is here.
Like every 1.0 release of a game, expect bugs. You can report them at https://github.com/coop-deluxe/sm64coopdx/issues

sm64coopdx is an official continuation of https://github.com/djoslin0/sm64ex-coop on sm64coopdx for the enhancements and progress it already has.
